{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.600", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.800", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.680", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.320", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor fast genau 99\u00a0Jahren hat Marie Juchacz als erste Frau im deutschen Parlament ihre Stimme erhoben und eine Rede gehalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.320", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie hat damals darauf hingewiesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.600", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das neugeschaffene Frauenwahlrecht keineswegs ein Anlass zur Dankbarkeit sei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.720", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern vielmehr eine Selbstverst\u00e4ndlichkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.560", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin froh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ich heute einem Parlament angeh\u00f6re, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem es selbstverst\u00e4ndlich ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.600", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass M\u00e4nner und Frauen ihre Stimme erheben und Gestaltungsrechte in diesem Parlament haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.200", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es ist heute eben noch nicht so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.840", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir in allen gesellschaftlichen Bereichen Gleichberechtigung erreicht haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.000", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb will ich f\u00fcr die SPD-Fraktion sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.360", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir h\u00f6ren erst auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.560", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber Gleichberechtigung zu streiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.080", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Frauen und M\u00e4nner die gleichen Rechte beim Sagen und beim Haben besitzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.400", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will Ihnen sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.240", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an welchen Punkten wir gro\u00dfen Handlungsbedarf sehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.560", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.280", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Sorgearbeit und die Erwerbsarbeit zwischen M\u00e4nnern und Frauen partnerschaftlich aufgeteilt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.000", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb haben wir in dem Koalitionsvertrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.160", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir mit CDU und CSU verhandelt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.600", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Riesenkapitel mit vielen Ma\u00dfnahmen zur Vereinbarkeit von Familie und Beruf aufgenommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.680", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber die SPD will noch einen Schritt weitergehen mit der Familienarbeitszeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.240", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Sorgearbeit mit kleinen Kindern und auch die Pflegearbeit partnerschaftlich aufzuteilen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.000", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb haben wir ein Recht auf befristete Teilzeit und ein R\u00fcckkehrrecht von Teilzeit auf Vollzeit vereinbart. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.520", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind froh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.280", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das in der n\u00e4chsten Koalition\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
