  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.320", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb wollen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Bezahlung in den typischen Frauenberufen und typischen M\u00e4nnerberufen angleicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.720", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.520", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Frauen das Gleiche verdienen wie M\u00e4nner. "
